We love the Sunnyvale Police Department!  
Always helping to spread awareness!

data.description:
‪Let's all work together to spread awareness on #HumanTrafficking. If you see something suspicious, or suspect someone is a victim of human trafficking, please report it to law enforcement. You never know whose life you could be saving. 

#HumanTraffickingAwarenessMonth‬

(National Center for Missing & Exploited Children, ERASE Child Trafficking)
